 Filter by amenities\\n\\n#### Popular\\n\\n* Free breakfast\\n  (15)\\n* Luxury\\n  (2)\\n* Pool\\n  (7)\\n #### Other amenities\\n\\n* Airport shuttle\\n  (1)\\n* Budget friendly\\n  (27)\\n* Connecting rooms\\n  (29)\\n* EV charging station\\n  (18)\\n* Extended stay\\n  (1)\\n* Family friendly\\n  (8)\\n* Kids eat free\\n  (12)\\n* Kitchen\\n  (1)\\n* Meeting facilities\\n  (33)\\n* Parking\\n  (31)\\n* Pets welcome\\n  (25)\\n* Restaurant on-site\\n  (33)\\n* Spa\\n  (1)\\n * Unselect all\\n\\n* Holiday Inn Birmingham City Centre\\n  \\n  #### [Holiday Inn Birmingham City Centre](https://www.ihg.com/holidayinn/hotels/us/en/birmingham/bhxwm/hoteldetail)\\n  \\n  Smallbrook  \\n  Birmingham, B5 4EW, United Kingdom\\n  \\n  0\\\\.19 mi (0.3 km) from Birmingham New Street Station\\n  \\n  4\\\\.11 [(2825 reviews)](https://www.ihg.com/holidayinn/hotels/us/en/birmingham/bhxwm/hoteldetail/hotel-reviews)\\n  \\n+ Pets Allowed\\n  \\n  From  \\n  /night\\n  \\n  Includes taxes and fees\\n  \\n  Excludes local taxes\\n  \\n  {baseAmount} room + {excludedFeeSubTotal} fees\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.easyhotel.com/explore/hotels-near-new-street-station\",\n      \"title\": \"Hotels near New Street Station, Birmingham\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Deals Explore Help\\n\\nGBP (£)\\n\\n##### Select Currency\\n\\n* GBP - Pound sterling\\n* USD - U.S. Dollar\\n* EUR - Euro\\n* CHF - Swiss franc\\n* AED - Dirham\\n* BRL - Brazilian Real\\n* CAD - Canadian Dollar\\n* RUB - Russian Ruble\\n* PLN - Polish złoty\\n* SEK - Swedish Krona\\n* AUD - Australian Dollar\\n* INR - Indian Rupee\\n* HUF - Hungarian Forint\\n\\nLog in Sign up\\n\\nExplore\\n\\n* Deals\\n* Explore\\n* Help\\n\\n* * *\\n\\nSettings\\n\\n* Language\\n  \\n  English Flag\\n  \\n  English\\n* Price display\\n  \\n  GBP £\\n\\n# Hotels near New Street Station\\n\\nBirmingham\\n\\nRight in the heart of [Birmingham](https://www.easyhotel.com/hotels/united-kingdom/birmingham) , New Street Station is the city’s main transport hub, making it super easy to get in and out by train. It’s surrounded by great shopping, buzzing restaurants, and loads of entertainment, so staying nearby means you’re never far from the action. Whether you’re visiting for work, a weekend break, or just passing through, hotels near New Street Station are the perfect spot to base yourself.\\n## Birmingham City Centre\\n\\nBirmingham Airport - 25 mins by taxi\\n\\nBirmingham New Street Station - 3 mins walk\\n\\nBirmingham coach station - 15 min walk\\n\\nExplore Hotel\\n\\n[**easyHotel Birmingham City Centre**](https://www.easyhotel.com/hotels/united-kingdom/birmingham/birmingham-city-centre) is only 0.2 miles from New Street Station - that’s just a quick 5-minute stroll. You’ll find us on John Bright Street, surrounded by lively bars, tasty places to eat, and some of Birmingham’s top sights. Our rooms are simple, clean, and comfy - ideal for getting a good night’s sleep after a busy day. With great value prices and 24-hour reception, we make city stays easy, whether you’re here for a show, a shopping trip, or an early train the next day.\\n\\n## Why Stay Near New Street Station, Birmingham?\\n\\nStaying near New Street Station makes everything a breeze. You’re just a short walk from the Bullring & Grand Central for shopping, plus the Birmingham Hippodrome and O2 Academy for top nights out.\\nFancy something tasty? Chinatown is nearby, packed with brilliant food spots. And with trains running all over the UK, you can get to London, Manchester or the airport in no time. It’s the ideal location to make the most of Birmingham without wasting a minute.\\n\\n[Part of thefamily of brands](https://easy.com)\\n\\nSubscribe to get the latest hotel deals and offers by email. I agree to receive marketing and promotion emails from easyHotel UK Limited and it’s group subsidiary companies as referenced in our website privacy policy\\n\\nSubscribe\\n\\nDownload Apps\\n\\n[](https://apps.apple.com/gb/app/easyhotel/id1492316252?mt=8) [](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.easyhotelapp.app&hl=en&pcampaignid=MKT-Other-global-all-co-prtnr-py-PartBadge-Mar2515-1)\\n\\nSite Map Terms & Conditions Cookie Policy Privacy Policy\\n\\nGive us a follow:\\n\\n[](https://www.facebook.com/easyHotel)\\n\\n[](https://www.instagram.com/easyhotel)\\n\\n[](https://www.linkedin.com/company/easyhotel-limited)\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://maps.google.com/maps/dir/\",\n      \"title\": \"Get directions for driving, transit, walking, and more - Directions, Traffic & Transit - Google Maps\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Open app\\n\\nFind a place\\n\\n\\n\\nYour location\\n\\nChoose starting point\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nChoose destination\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n Leave now\\n\\nOptions\\n\\nYour location\\n\\nTrails\\n\\nDedicated lanes\\n\\nBicycle-friendly roads\\n\\nDirt/unpaved trails\\n\\nLive traffic\\n\\nFast\\n\\nSlow\\n\\nTraffic Transit Bicycling Satellite Terrain Wildfires Air Quality Map movement controls Real-time location sharing Your contributions Your places\\n\\n* Settings\\n* Language\\n* Help\\n* My Maps\\n* Send Product Feedback\\n\\nGlobal edit\\n\\n# Settings\\n\\n# Settings\\n\\n* Google Location Settings\\n* Privacy Policy\\n* Terms of Service\\n* Region Settings\\n* 20260527\\\\_0\\n\\nOpen the Google Maps app?\\n\\nGet real-time navigation and more in the Maps app\\n\\nContinue Keep using web\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.rome2rio.com/s/Birmingham-New-Street-Station/Hyatt-Regency-Birmingham\",\n      \"title\": \"Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"[Rome2Rio](https://www.rome2rio.com/)\\n\\n# How to get from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham by tram bus taxi walk by tram, bus, taxi or foot\\n\\n## Find Transport to Hyatt Regency Birmingham\\n\\nTravel from\\n\\nTo\\n\\nSee all options\\n\\nSearch accommodation with Expedia\\n\\n* Search\\n* Transport\\n* FAQs\\n* Map\\n* Operators\\n\\nExplore\\n\\n## There are 4 ways to get from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham by tram, bus, taxi, or foot\\n\\nSelect an option below to see step-by-step directions and to compare ticket prices and travel times in Rome2Rio's travel planner.\\n\\n1. ### Tram best 1. Take the tram from Grand Central to Centenary Square tram Metro 9 min\\n2. ### Line 23 bus cheapest 1. Take the bus from Bus Mall to Library Metro Stop bus 822 / ... 14 min $2–4\\n3. ### Taxi 1. Take the taxi from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham taxi 4,340 ft 2 min $5–7\\n4. ### Walk 1.\\nTake the foot from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham walk 3,750 ft 13 min\\n\\n### Questions & Answers\\n\\nWhat is the cheapest way to get from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham?\\n\\nThe cheapest way to get from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham is to line 23 bus which costs $2 - $4 and takes 14 min.\\n\\n[More details](https://www.rome2rio.com/map/Birmingham-New-Street-Station/Hyatt-Regency-Birmingham?route%3DLine-23-bus)\\n\\nWhat is the fastest way to get from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham?\\n\\nThe fastest way to get from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham is to taxi which takes 2 min and costs $5 - $7.\\n\\n[More details](https://www.rome2rio.com/map/Birmingham-New-Street-Station/Hyatt-Regency-Birmingham?route%3DTaxi)\\n\\nIs there a direct bus between Birmingham New Street Station and Hyatt Regency Birmingham?\\nYes, there is a direct bus departing from Bus Mall and arriving at Library Metro Stop. Services depart every five minutes, and operate every day. The journey takes approximately 7 min.\\n\\n[More details](https://www.rome2rio.com/map/Birmingham-New-Street-Station/Hyatt-Regency-Birmingham?route%3DTram)\\n\\nIs there a direct train between Birmingham New Street Station and Hyatt Regency Birmingham?\\n\\nYes, there is a direct train departing from Grand Central and arriving at Centenary Square. Services depart every 10 minutes, and operate every day. The journey takes approximately 5 min.\\n\\n[More details](https://www.rome2rio.com/map/Birmingham-New-Street-Station/Hyatt-Regency-Birmingham?route%3DTram)\\n\\nHow far is it from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham?\\n\\nThe distance between Birmingham New Street Station and Hyatt Regency Birmingham is 2972 feet.\\n\\nHow do I travel from Birmingham New Street Station to Hyatt Regency Birmingham without a car?\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://maps.apple.com/\",\n      \"title\": \"Apple Maps: Directions, Guides & Traffic\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"A\\n\\nStandard\\n\\nHybrid\\n\\nSatellite\\n\\nYour location can only be shown when location services are enabled and you are connected to the Internet. [Learn More](https://support.apple.com/guide/mac-help/allow-apps-to-detect-the-location-of-your-mac-mh35873/mac)\\n\\nN\\n\\n[Privacy](https://www.apple.com/privacy/) [Terms](https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/maps/terms-en.html) [Legal](https://gspe21-ssl.ls.apple.com/html/attribution.html) [Imagery](https://maps.apple.com/imagecollection)\\n\\nReport an Issue\\n\\nDone\\n\\nN\\n\\n[Privacy](https://www.apple.com/privacy/) [Terms](https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/maps/terms-en.html) [Legal](https://gspe21-ssl.ls.apple.com/html/attribution.html) [Imagery](https://maps.apple.com/imagecollection)\\n\\n# Apple Maps\\n\\nSearch Guides Directions\\n\\nHave a Business on Maps?\\n\\n[Manage Your Business](https://businessconnect.apple.com/?utm_source=maps.apple.com)\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://maps.google.com/\",\n      \"ti